    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. The CFD hemolysis model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Note: this package conforms to the Minimal profile; a structured ContextOfUse object has not been provided, and intended-use scope is conveyed through the package description and validation narrative only.",
